283
00:16:58,780 --> 00:17:01,450
You…Why do you speak so fast?

284
00:17:04,089 --> 00:17:05,510
That’s true indeed.

285
00:17:06,940 --> 00:17:09,510
But stop daydreaming.

286
00:17:10,220 --> 00:17:10,910
Do you know why our college

287
00:17:10,910 --> 00:17:12,300
is named Charlotte?

288
00:17:12,550 --> 00:17:13,510
Why?

289
00:17:14,630 --> 00:17:17,790
It means Xia (Char)Yuanqing and Gu Yanluo (Lo)
are a perfect match

290
00:17:17,790 --> 00:17:19,060
and a strong couple.

291
00:17:19,740 --> 00:17:20,750
Do you get it?

292
00:17:21,630 --> 00:17:22,550
Yes.

293
00:17:23,260 --> 00:17:25,690
Turns out you are a couple fan.

294
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:30,390
Rest easy. How can Prince Charming fall for me?

295
00:17:32,060 --> 00:17:33,790
You have some self-knowledge.

296
00:17:34,060 --> 00:17:37,270
Don’t think you can make a difference
by changing your hairstyle.

297
00:17:37,270 --> 00:17:38,510
In my eyes,

298
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:40,060
only Xia Yuanqing

299
00:17:40,060 --> 00:17:42,150
is the perfect Princess Charming.

300
00:17:42,150 --> 00:17:44,550
Only she can be a match for Prince Charming.

301
00:17:44,820 --> 00:17:47,460
