302
00:17:49,670 --> 00:17:50,550
Yes.

303
00:17:54,390 --> 00:17:56,060
I’m not angry.

304
00:17:56,550 --> 00:17:57,510
I must be calm.

305
00:17:57,630 --> 00:17:59,390
I am Ye Zhenhan now.

306
00:17:59,510 --> 00:18:01,150
I am a lady.

307
00:18:22,230 --> 00:18:23,220
[Message from Yan Jiuyue]
Zhenhan, are you there?

308
00:18:23,220 --> 00:18:24,210
[I did part-time work at the library today.
