430
00:24:20,990 --> 00:24:22,750
Yes. My mother also says

431
00:24:23,060 --> 00:24:24,420
she won’t let me go to work

432
00:24:24,420 --> 00:24:25,820
if I don’t teach you well.

433
00:24:27,660 --> 00:24:28,390
Gu Yanluo,

434
00:24:28,630 --> 00:24:30,220
