435
00:24:30,630 --> 00:24:31,390
Yanluo.

436
00:24:36,270 --> 00:24:37,930
It seems you are very popular.

437
00:24:38,060 --> 00:24:40,820
Look, you are quite handsome indeed.

438
00:24:40,990 --> 00:24:43,050
