441
00:24:46,910 --> 00:24:48,990
Choose me.

442
00:25:04,670 --> 00:25:05,510
Her.

443
00:25:12,990 --> 00:25:13,910
OK.

444
00:25:16,140 --> 00:25:17,060
Gu Yanluo,

445
00:25:17,460 --> 00:25:18,580
are we enemies?

446
00:25:18,910 --> 00:25:19,940
Didn’t we agree yesterday

447
00:25:19,940 --> 00:25:21,340
to mind our own business?

448
00:25:21,700 --> 00:25:24,550
OK. Gu Yanluo, Ye Zhenhan.

449
00:25:24,620 --> 00:25:26,150
You two will be in a group then.

450
00:25:26,150 --> 00:25:28,990
Very well chosen.
A combination of straight A students.

451
00:25:28,990 --> 00:25:29,990
Very well chosen.

452
00:25:30,630 --> 00:25:32,990
I am Yanluo’s girlfriend.

453
00:25:33,150 --> 00:25:35,340
