457
00:26:00,210 --> 00:26:02,580
Narcissus, pretentious death.

458
00:26:03,180 --> 00:26:04,110
What did you say?

459
00:26:05,270 --> 00:26:06,550
No…nothing.

460
00:26:07,150 --> 00:26:10,510
I complimented you are handsome immortal
on the altar.

461
00:26:10,790 --> 00:26:12,990
I complimented you as Prince Charming.

462
